All Classes and Interfaces

Class
Description
FileMngr
This is the main model class, contains all the implementations of the CRUD operations.
Main
The starter class of the application
MainController
The class MainController is used as the main brain of the application, manages button triggers and calls their actions thanks to the ActionListener interface.
MainView
This is the main and only UI class, stores and sets up all the swing elements.
Person
This is the main and only bean of the application, holds the user data.
PersonDAO
This interface contains all the CRUD operations and some other utilities used when working with the file.
